## 4) First use (quick start)

1. Power the board via USB
2. Confirm OLED splash appears
3. Inject CW audio into the configured ADC pin (default GPIO4)
4. Use **Calibrate** to lock onto the tone
5. Watch decoded output on OLED and/or Web UI

