## 12) Safety / sanity notes

- Do not exceed ADC voltage limits (0–3.3V).
- Use AC coupling + bias network.
- Keep wires short and avoid noisy power supplies if you can.
- If you’re feeding from a radio speaker output, consider a divider and/or an isolation transformer.

